content: A great place to go to to have a break from the life’s chaos. It is also at the base of the mountain so it has easy access to hiking trails.
It's spacious and great for a walk/picnic. If you have a dog, it's great for a walk.

The two lakes located in the middle of the city are large and well organized, so it seems to be really good for walking or exercising. There are many people and there are many places to go to cafes around the lake.
There are two lakes between the apartment forests. It is a space where you can walk around and sit while looking at the scenery.
